Ways to treat and prevent depression

Talk to someone preferably a counsellor 
physical exercises 
meditate 
have even rest and sleep
eat well
join a support group 
try to find new positive hobbies 
hang out more with positive friends

Depression⚠️

Extreme sadness to the point of feeling numb for atleast 2weeks
loss of interest in life
social withdrawal 
low self-esteem 
lack of concentration/randomly zoning out
if you notice these signs please seek 4 help or talk to someone.  if your friend has them help them
